								p Chad Boggs joins NAI Ohio Equities after spending more than 15 years in information technology in the logistics and retail sectors. As a small business owner, Chad has experience as both a landlord and commercial tenant, which led to the discovery of his passion for commercial real estate. He hopes to use this passion to help others achieve their financial goals through real estate.
